The paper deals with ontology-mediated querying, which is a topic that falls under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and databases (cs.DB). The use of description logics (DLs) also suggests that the paper could be classified under logic in computer science (cs.LO) and computational complexity (cs.CC). Finally, the paper's focus on the data complexity of queries suggests that it could also be classified under data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
